data.description: OPEN SATURDAY 1-3pm! Welcome home to this charming ranch-style gem in the sought-after Millard area! Step onto the inviting front porch and feel the warmth of this cozy abode. With new carpeting throughout and convenient main floor laundry, comfort and convenience are at your fingertips. The vaulted ceilings enhance the open and airy living room, complete with a cozy stone fireplace and soft ambient lighting for relaxing evenings. Retreat to the spacious primary suite boasting a large closet and en suite bathroom. Priced below neighborhood comparables, this home offers incredible value with the potential for instant equity through minor updates. The fully finished basement provides plenty of extra living space & ample storage space, while the backyard oasis beckons with a spacious deck, a shed, & flat, full privacy fenced yard. With its prime location close to amenities, shopping, dining, & major transportation routes, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience!
